Docs.remarks:
In .NET Framework, this namespace contains classes and interfaces that enable browser-server communication. These classes include
      the  class, which provides extensive information about the current HTTP request;
      the  class, which manages HTTP output to the client;
      and the  class, which provides access to server-side utilities and processes.
       also includes classes for cookie manipulation, file transfer, exception information, and output cache control in .NET Framework.
